Summary: Taking photos of star trails, got a weird path obviously not a star.
divs: Sighting DetailsI was taking star trail photos. various exposure times. most of the photos were normal looking. some bumps in the trails seeing as my camera was on the ground. But in this photo it is whirling all over, and seems to be a signature of sorts. if all the star trails did the same thing, I would debunk this as the camera was shaken... this is an UNALTERED photo. I added another photo from the same set of shots as a guide line to what they all looked like.
